data.description: Welcome to this adorable ONE LEVEL home with spacious bonus room up that includes such inviting features from the minute you drive up!  This adorable 3-bedroom, 3 full bath home will wow you from the moment you walk in.  The main level boasts all 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, including an open floor plan with large living room space, gas fireplace to enjoy that evening glass of wine as the colder months approach, kitchen with all stainless appliances, gas range, stainless farm sink, granite counters and pantry closet.  Master on main includes full bath, double sinks and walk in closet. The second level bonus room provides ample space for SO MUCH!  Make it a playroom, office, media room, craft room OR wall it off to make a 4th BR.  You will also love it includes a full bath as well!  Just off the kitchen, step onto your covered patio, which includes outlets to hang a TV, and an extra paved space perfect for grilling out!  The backyard is fully fenced in and ready for you to make it your own.  As if this isn't enough, this home is located on a cul-de-sac street and is conveniently located to so much Greenville offers.  Conestee Park which includes hiking trails, mountain biking trails, playgrounds, dog park and more, is less than 5 minutes away, shopping and dining on Woodruff Rd is 10 mins away, downtown is less than 15 and the interstate is less than 10 minutes!  Don't blink or this will be gone...schedule a showing today! SELLER OFFERING PAINT ALLOWANCE for cabinets with acceptable offer!
